## 2026-04-03 - AnalyticsPanel validation results go stale after fixes are applied without auto-revalidation
- Added `tokenChangeKey` prop (number) to `AnalyticsPanel`. App.tsx increments it in `refreshAll` (which is called on every SSE token change, editor save, and mutation). In `AnalyticsPanel`, a new `useEffect` on `tokenChangeKey` immediately marks `resultsStale = true` and schedules a debounced `runValidate()` after 2s (cancels if another change arrives within the window). A mutable `validateResultsRef` tracks whether validation has run yet, so the auto-revalidate is skipped on the very first load (when `validateResults === null`).
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/App.tsx` ~L350, ~L2224; `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/AnalyticsPanel.tsx` ~L26, ~L67, ~L100, ~L148
